data.description: This bright and airy 3 bedroom home, is centrally located close to downtown, I-95, shops & dining at 5-points and River City Marketplace. This ranch-style home offers a gorgeous kitchen, with brand new appliances and washer & dryer conveying. It also features tons of other updates including a new roof in 2022, interior and exterior fresh paint and modern lighting. You will also notice the enclosed porch and covered back porch adds functionality and privacy. This truly is a gem under $200K!
